H0.text: Who was the Poet Laureate at the time of the Coronation of Queen Elizabeth II. John Betjeman

H1.text: Who was the Poet Laureate at the time of the Coronation of Queen Elizabeth II. W.H. Auden

H2.text: Who was the Poet Laureate at the time of the Coronation of Queen Elizabeth II. Cecil Day-Lewis

H3.text: Who was the Poet Laureate at the time of the Coronation of Queen Elizabeth II. Masefieldian

A4.text: Betjeman became Poet Laureate in 1972 following the death of Day-Lewis

A5.text: Betjeman was considered as a candidate to be the new Poet Laureate of the United Kingdom in 1967, following the death of John Masefield
